---
title: Curried Chicken Salad Wraps with Golden Raisins & Shredded Carrots
description: This lunch is (quite literally) gold! A mix of sour cream, mayo, and curry spices coat chicken and golden raisins in creamy, golden-hued flavor. The chicken salad is then stuffed inside steamy tortillas and topped with shredded carrots for even more crunch and color. Glorious texture, rich flavors, brilliant hues—yep, that’s a solid (gold) wrap!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/curried-chicken-salad-wraps-f2916b4a.jpg
